{"tid":454402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大種乞衣】立法會續審一地兩檢　多個工會請願冀議員勿拉布","createTime":"2017-11-01T05:48:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T10:33:48.000Z","uid":37661,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"23ce06f6e5b9c449d7ea3cc118463e55a61a0801","tid":454402,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"立法會續審一地兩檢　多個工會請願冀議員勿拉布<br />\n2017-11-01 HKT 11:14<br />\n<br />\n立法會今日繼續審議政府提出的高鐵「一地兩檢」無約束力議案，工聯會、鐵路工會和旅遊聯業工會到立法會請願，支持高鐵「一地兩檢」。<br />\n<br />\n他們說，希望反對派議員不要拉布，期望立法會盡快審議方案，令高鐵能如期在明年第3季通車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362409-20171101.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362409-20171101.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=79819c0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1362409-20171101.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a088821a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1362409-20171101.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e8cf0212e5228cc7450ed385de0e72db617e4858","tid":454402,"uid":19213,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"賣港死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c7437fb219b3e8ec18b3f1cf2cc288c8f9c9f5","tid":454402,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:36:03.000Z","msg":"3個都叫多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3c3b3e05f3782939ce8b526df346f698e21795","tid":454402,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:38:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f0a23777cf6d25cc430b82cc9e913038c12b11b","tid":454402,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望議員專重民意唔好拉布<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"fo